{"id": 465, "name": "Projet de loi de finances pour 2025, n\u00b0\u00a0324", "url": "/dyn/17/amendements/0324A/AN/465", "date": "2024-10-16", "status": "Rejet\u00e9", "proposed_by": [{"first_name": "Nicolas", "last_name": "Sansu", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Emmanuel", "last_name": "Maurel", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Emmanuel", "last_name": "Tjibaou", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Soumya", "last_name": "Bourouaha", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "\u00c9douard", "last_name": "B\u00e9nard", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Victor", "last_name": "Castor", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Andr\u00e9", "last_name": "Chassaigne", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Elsa", "last_name": "Faucillon", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "\u00c9meline", "last_name": "K/Bidi", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Karine", "last_name": "Lebon", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Paul", "last_name": "Lecoq", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric", "last_name": "Maillot", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Yannick", "last_name": "Monnet", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Marcellin", "last_name": "Nadeau", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "St\u00e9phane", "last_name": "Peu", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Mereana", "last_name": "Reid Arbelot", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Davy", "last_name": "Rimane", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}], "summary": "Cet amendement vise \u00e0 utiliser comme r\u00e9f\u00e9rence pour la contribution diff\u00e9rentielle une fraction du patrimoine net taxable plut\u00f4t qu\u2019une qu\u2019une fraction du revenu. En effet, bien que ce dispositif soit louable, il semble limit\u00e9 car le revenu fiscal de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence est une donn\u00e9e facilement manipulable, notamment pour les contribuables les plus ais\u00e9s (notamment via l\u2019usage de holding personnelles qui permettent de stocker les revenus). Le patrimoine \u00e9tant moins facilement manipulable, le dispositif propos\u00e9 permettra de mieux toucher les milliardaires qui, en l\u2019\u00e9tat, serait peu touch\u00e9s.\nCet amendement fixe le plancher \u00e0 2% du patrimoine net."}